---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Comunidad Osbord" description="Forma parte de la comunidad privada de egresados del Instituto Online Osbord. Networking global, mentoría directa y bolsa de empleo exclusiva.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-brand-navy py-20 lg:py-24 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-brand-navy-light"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-gold/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-6">
        <span class="section-label">Ecosistema Exclusivo</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Comunidad <span class="text-brand-gold">Osbord</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Más que un título, una red de profesionales de alto nivel. Como alumno Osbord, accedes a un ecosistema diseñado para potenciar tu carrera.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-8 bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl border border-gray-100 space-y-4 text-center hover:shadow-elevated transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Networking Global</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Conecta con empresarios y profesionales de alto nivel en más de 10 países de habla hispana.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl border border-gray-100 space-y-4 text-center hover:shadow-elevated transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="m15.75 10.5 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v11.38a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72M4.5 18.75h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-9A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Sesiones Q&A en Vivo</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Sesiones mensuales de preguntas y respuestas con especialistas activos de cada industria.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl border border-gray-100 space-y-4 text-center hover:shadow-elevated transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20.25 14.15v4.25c0 1.094-.787 2.036-1.872 2.18-2.087.277-4.216.42-6.378.42s-4.291-.143-6.378-.42c-1.085-.144-1.872-1.086-1.872-2.18v-4.25m16.5 0a2.18 2.18 0 0 0 .75-1.661V8.706c0-1.081-.768-2.015-1.837-2.175a48.114 48.114 0 0 0-3.413-.387m4.5 8.006c-.194.165-.42.295-.673.38A23.978 23.978 0 0 1 12 15.75c-2.648 0-5.195-.429-7.577-1.22a2.016 2.016 0 0 1-.673-.38m0 0A2.18 2.18 0 0 1 3 12.489V8.706c0-1.081.768-2.015 1.837-2.175a48.111 48.111 0 0 1 3.413-.387m7.5 0V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 13.5 3h-3a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v.894m7.5 0a48.667 48.667 0 0 0-7.5 0M12 12.75h.008v.008H12v-.008Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Bolsa de Empleo</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Ofertas laborales curadas exclusivamente para egresados del Instituto Osbord a nivel internacional.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection headline="Únete a la comunidad Osbord" subtext="Al matricularte en cualquiera de nuestros másters, accedes automáticamente a todos los beneficios de la comunidad." buttonText="SOLICITAR ADMISIÓN" />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
